Can you tell them I'll be right there?

122
00:07:13,935 --> 00:07:18,900
Yeah, sure.

123
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:23,700
Oh.
- Hey Lynette. So is Tom almost ready?

124
00:07:23,735 --> 00:07:26,700
Yeah, he's just getting his briefcase.

125
00:07:26,735 --> 00:07:31,700
Oh, sorry.
- OK.

126
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:43,600
