159
00:09:38,035 --> 00:09:41,100
I can't wait.

160
00:09:41,135 --> 00:09:42,000
Mmmh.

161
00:09:42,035 --> 00:09:44,100
Oh, is that fennel seed? It's fantastic!

162
00:09:44,135 --> 00:09:48,800
I don't know, but anything that good has got to be sinful.

163
